print("X l D liu (Filling NaNs, Feature Engineering)")

# X l gi tr b thiu (Missing Values)
# Age: in bng gi tr trung v (median)
data['Age'] = data['Age'].fillna(data['Age'].median())

# Embarked: in bng gi tr xut hin nhiu nht (mode)
data['Embarked'] = data['Embarked'].fillna(data['Embarked'].mode()[0])

# To c trng mi (Feature Engineering)
# To bin 'Has_Cabin' (C Cabin hay khng)
data['Has_Cabin'] = data['Cabin'].notnull().astype(int)

# To bin 'log_Fare' (v 'Fare' b lch)
data['log_Fare'] = data['Fare'].apply(lambda x: np.log10(x + 1))

#To FamilySize
data['FamilySize'] = data['SibSp'] + data['Parch'] + 1

drop_cols = ['Name', 'Ticket', 'Cabin']
data = data.drop(columns=drop_cols)

In[32]:
cv = KFold(n_splits=10, shuffle=True, random_state=42)
accuracies = []
max_attributes = len(data.columns) - 1  # tr ct target
depth_range = range(1, max_attributes + 1)

for depth in depth_range:
    fold_accuracy = []
    tree_model = tree.DecisionTreeClassifier(max_depth=depth, random_state=42)
    for train_idx, valid_idx in cv.split(data):
        f_train = data.iloc[train_idx]
        f_valid = data.iloc[valid_idx]

        tree_model.fit(f_train.drop('Survived', axis=1), f_train['Survived'])
        acc = tree_model.score(f_valid.drop('Survived', axis=1), f_valid['Survived'])
        fold_accuracy.append(acc)
    
    avg_acc = sum(fold_accuracy) / len(fold_accuracy)
    accuracies.append(avg_acc)

# Hin th kt qu cross-validation
df_cv = pd.DataFrame({"Max Depth": depth_range, "Average Accuracy": accuracies})
print(df_cv.to_string(index=False))
